-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| CHAPTER 1 - GETTING STARTED                                         |
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

- Starting DataStax Studio

    1. Run the shell script to start Studio.

         $ cd /usr/local/bin/datastax-studio-6.8.21
         $ ./bin/server.sh


    2. To run Studio, navigate to:

         http://127.0.0.1:9091


    3. To stop Studio:

         $ pkill -f studio